dict.string: Collection of participant-provided information through a mobile device app for use in drup safety research

The data captured from pregnant women (e.g. medical product exposures, outcomes etc.) will be linked with data from an organization, such as a clinical practise, that has access to electronic health data and this will help provide insights into the efficacy and safety of medical products.
